com.facebook.zookeeper

Interface ZooKeeperIface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicZooKeeper, MockZooKeeper, RecoveringZooKeeper

    public interface ZooKeeperIface
    ZooKeeper interface limited to some basic operations. More ZooKeeper methods may be added to this interface as needed. See ZooKeeper API for documentation.
